10// FastEmit Immediate Predicate functions.
11static bool Predicate_ImmI8(int64_t Imm) {
12return -(1 << (8 - 1)) <= Imm && Imm < (1 << (8 - 1));
13}
14static bool Predicate_ImmI16(int64_t Imm) {
15return -(1 << (16 - 1)) <= Imm && Imm < (1 << (16 - 1));
16}
17static bool Predicate_LaneIdx32(int64_t Imm) {
18return 0 <= Imm && Imm < 32;
19}
20static bool Predicate_LaneIdx16(int64_t Imm) {
21return 0 <= Imm && Imm < 16;
22}
23static bool Predicate_LaneIdx8(int64_t Imm) {
24return 0 <= Imm && Imm < 8;
25}
26static bool Predicate_LaneIdx4(int64_t Imm) {
27return 0 <= Imm && Imm < 4;
28}
29static bool Predicate_LaneIdx2(int64_t Imm) {
30return 0 <= Imm && Imm < 2;
31}

951// Top-level FastEmit function.
952
953unsigned fastEmit_r(MVT VT, MVT RetVT, unsigned Opcode, unsigned Op0, bool Op0IsKill) override {
954 switch (Opcode) {
955 case ISD::ABS: return fastEmit_ISD_ABS_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
956 case ISD::ANY_EXTEND: return fastEmit_ISD_ANY_EXTEND_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
957 case ISD::BITCAST: return fastEmit_ISD_BITCAST_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
958 case ISD::CTLZ: return fastEmit_ISD_CTLZ_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
959 case ISD::CTPOP: return fastEmit_ISD_CTPOP_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
960 case ISD::CTTZ: return fastEmit_ISD_CTTZ_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
961 case ISD::FABS: return fastEmit_ISD_FABS_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
962 case ISD::FCEIL: return fastEmit_ISD_FCEIL_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
963 case ISD::FFLOOR: return fastEmit_ISD_FFLOOR_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
964 case ISD::FNEARBYINT: return fastEmit_ISD_FNEARBYINT_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
965 case ISD::FNEG: return fastEmit_ISD_FNEG_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
966 case ISD::FP_EXTEND: return fastEmit_ISD_FP_EXTEND_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
967 case ISD::FP_ROUND: return fastEmit_ISD_FP_ROUND_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
968 case ISD::FP_TO_SINT: return fastEmit_ISD_FP_TO_SINT_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
969 case ISD::FP_TO_UINT: return fastEmit_ISD_FP_TO_UINT_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
970 case ISD::FRINT: return fastEmit_ISD_FRINT_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
971 case ISD::FSQRT: return fastEmit_ISD_FSQRT_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
972 case ISD::FTRUNC: return fastEmit_ISD_FTRUNC_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
973 case ISD::SCALAR_TO_VECTOR: return fastEmit_ISD_SCALAR_TO_VECTOR_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
974 case ISD::SIGN_EXTEND: return fastEmit_ISD_SIGN_EXTEND_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
975 case ISD::SINT_TO_FP: return fastEmit_ISD_SINT_TO_FP_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
976 case ISD::TRUNCATE: return fastEmit_ISD_TRUNCATE_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
977 case ISD::UINT_TO_FP: return fastEmit_ISD_UINT_TO_FP_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
978 case ISD::ZERO_EXTEND: return fastEmit_ISD_ZERO_EXTEND_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
979 case WebAssemblyISD::BR_TABLE: return fastEmit_WebAssemblyISD_BR_TABLE_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
980 case WebAssemblyISD::WIDEN_HIGH_S: return fastEmit_WebAssemblyISD_WIDEN_HIGH_S_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
981 case WebAssemblyISD::WIDEN_HIGH_U: return fastEmit_WebAssemblyISD_WIDEN_HIGH_U_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
982 case WebAssemblyISD::WIDEN_LOW_S: return fastEmit_WebAssemblyISD_WIDEN_LOW_S_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
983 case WebAssemblyISD::WIDEN_LOW_U: return fastEmit_WebAssemblyISD_WIDEN_LOW_U_r(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill);
984 default: return 0;
985 }

2011
2012// Top-level FastEmit function.
2013
2014unsigned fastEmit_rr(MVT VT, MVT RetVT, unsigned Opcode, unsigned Op0, bool Op0IsKill, unsigned Op1, bool Op1IsKill) override {
2015 switch (Opcode) {
2016 case ISD::ADD: return fastEmit_ISD_ADD_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
2017 case ISD::AND: return fastEmit_ISD_AND_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
2018 case ISD::FADD: return fastEmit_ISD_FADD_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
2019 case ISD::FCOPYSIGN: return fastEmit_ISD_FCOPYSIGN_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
2020 case ISD::FDIV: return fastEmit_ISD_FDIV_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
2021 case ISD::FMAXIMUM: return fastEmit_ISD_FMAXIMUM_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
2022 case ISD::FMINIMUM: return fastEmit_ISD_FMINIMUM_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
2023 case ISD::FMUL: return fastEmit_ISD_FMUL_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
2024 case ISD::FSUB: return fastEmit_ISD_FSUB_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
2025 case ISD::MUL: return fastEmit_ISD_MUL_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
2026 case ISD::OR: return fastEmit_ISD_OR_rr(VT, RetVT, Op0, Op0IsKill, Op1, Op1IsKill);
